, holotype, distal part of left humerus. Skaerum MØlle, Jutland, Denmark, Gram Formation (late Miocene, early-middle Tortonian, 8.0–11.5 ma); GM1: 
<emphasis id="B90DEAB3D178FFCA6B2F2E8CFC5EFAE5" box="[894,921,1277,1298]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="428">2A</emphasis>
