<taxonomicName id="4C794D22D178FFCA68AB2F43FE70FAB0" authorityName="Van Beneden" authorityYear="1877" box="[250,439,1330,1351]" class="Mammalia" family="Phocidae" genus="Platyphoca" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="9" pageNumber="428" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="B90DEAB3D178FFCA68AB2F43FE70FAB0" box="[250,439,1330,1351]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="428">Platyphoca vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, дистальная часть левой плечевой кости; из Ли-Крик, формация Йорктаун (плиоцен, 5.0–5.8 млн лет назад); по: 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE84B50D178FFCA6A652F3DFD3AFA95" author="Koretsky, I. A. &amp; Ray, C. E." box="[564,765,1356,1378]" pageId="9" pageNumber="428" pagination="81 - 140" refId="ref9574" refString="Koretsky, I. A., Ray, C. E. Phocidae of the Pliocene of eastern USA // Geology and paleontology of the Lee Creek Mine, North Carolina IV / Eds C. E. Ray, D. A. Bohaska, I. A. Koretsky et al. - Virginia Museum of Natural History, 2008. - 15 (Special Publication). - P. 81 - 140." type="book chapter" year="2008">Koretsky, Ray (2008</bibRefCitation>
